  "texts": [
    "The results of our study show that a coherent story concept can be created within one chatbot, moving smoothly from general to specific.",
    "ChatGPT's ability to produce a huge amount of coherent text will allow the writer to focus mainly on developing a unique and original idea, not spending time on monotonous work.",
    "If the AI agent's peculiarities are considered, the process of AI-assisted writing will be successful and pleasant for the human author.",
    "We understand that chatbot cannot completely replace the writer because unique cognitive processes take place in the writer's head, which cannot be reproduced by AI technologies.",
    "Apart from this, creative writing, from poetry to journalism, is at the crux of human ingenuity and social interaction."
